.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, accountant, journalist, engineer
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the engineer is between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the engineer and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the accountant is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the journalist is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Job   | analyst      | accountant  | engineer  | journalist |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

