.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-8::.
City: edinburgh, san-francisco, rome, liverpool
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, zombie
4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, horse, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, quad-bike, subway
1. the person watching drama movies is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the car##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person traveling to rome is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| City      | rome  | liverpool   | edinburgh    | san-francisco  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | drama   | documentary | satire |
| Pet           | cat       | horse   | frog        | snake  |
| Transport     | quad-bike | jet-ski | car         | subway |

